ActHazardous Products Act
SubjectResidential Detectors Regulations
PrecisResidential Detectors Regulations, to update the health and safety requirements for domestic detectors to reflect the current versions of ULC standards, as amended from time to time. The new standards are harmonized with the Underwriters' Laboratories standards used in the United States.
